TELEGRAM_CALL_TO_ACTION=Follow for daily UPSC/SSC current affairs, exam-focused summaries, and quick MCQ practice.
TELEGRAM_DISCOVERY_KEYWORDS=UPSC current affairs, SSC current affairs, daily current affairs, current affairs quiz, government exam preparation, GK updates
GROUP_ANSWER_DELAY_MINUTES=30
GROUP_DISCUSSION_CALL_TO_ACTION=Reply with your reason or one keyword you would revise from this topic.

